{"word":"G2021 - ἐπιχειρέω - epicheiréō - ep-ee-khi-reh'-o - Go about","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιχειρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epicheiréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-khi-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go about</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எத்தனம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"1. to put the hand to"},{"paragraph":"2. to take in hand, undertake, attempt"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5495 - χείρ - cheír - khire/5495\">G5495</a>; to put the <i>hand upon</i>, that is, <i>undertake:</i> - go about, take in hand (upon).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}